SUMMARY:Interchange Message: WEMBLEY PARK STATION: Friday 12\, Saturday 
 13\, Wednesday 17\, Friday 19\, Saturday 20\, Tuesday 23\, Friday 26\, 
 Saturday 27 and Monday 29 June\, Wednesday 1\, Friday 3 and Saturday 4 
 July\, between 2230 and 2325 each evening\, the station will be busy due 
 to Harry Styles concerts at Wembley Stadium. The Bridge Road entrance will
  be exit only until the queue to enter the station clears. Entry to the 
 station\, including step-free access via lift\, will be via Olympic Way. 
 Please allow extra time for your journey
END:VEVENT
